    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The psychological process of experiencing devotional feelings in a private sphere, whether or not encouraged by the church authorities, often with the aid of texts, figurines or images.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000303/ANET</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000110115/Anet, working group AAT</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Het psychologische proces van het beleven van devotionele gevoelens in de privésfeer, al dan niet aangemoedigd door de kerkelijke autoriteit, vaak met behulp van teksten, beelden of afbeeldingen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
